================================================================================
Model weights (NOT distributed by Gemma4SwiftCore)
================================================================================

Gemma4SwiftCore loads model weights at runtime from HuggingFace Hub via
the standard mlx-swift-lm download client. The Gemma 4 weights themselves
are published by Google under the Gemma Terms of Use:

  https://ai.google.dev/gemma/terms

Users of Gemma4SwiftCore are responsible for complying with the Gemma
Terms of Use when downloading, using, or redistributing the model weights.
Gemma4SwiftCore neither modifies nor redistributes the weights.
